OL,3,CBishop 'sorry' for failing to
OL,4,C'rigorously' pursue abuse claims
OL,6,FThe Bishop of Lincoln has insisted he
OL,7,Fdid all he could to report abuse
OL,8,Fallegations against a prolific
OL,9,Fpaedophile, but has apologised for
OL,10,Ffailing to "rigorously" pursue the
OL,11,Fclaims.
OL,13,FRight Reverend Stephen Conway was
OL,14,FBishop of Ely in 2013 when he was told
OL,15,Fdetails of John Smyth's abuse.
