OL,3,CBishop 'sorry' for failing to
OL,4,C'rigorously' pursue abuse claims
OL,6,FA report published last week found
OL,7,FSmyth, a barrister, had abused more
OL,8,Fthan 100 children and young men in the
OL,9,FUK and Africa during an association
OL,10,Fwith the Church of England spanning
OL,11,Ffive decades.
OL,13,FThe Makin report concluded Smyth, who
OL,14,Fdied in 2018 while under police
OL,15,Finvestigation, might have been brought
OL,16,Fto justice had the Archbishop of
OL,17,FCanterbury Justin Welby formally
OL,18,Freported him to police a decade ago.
