OL,3,CBishop 'sorry' for failing to
OL,4,C'rigorously' pursue abuse claims
OL,6,FWelby announced his resignation over
OL,7,Fthe issue on Tuesday afternoon, saying
OL,8,Fthe report had "renewed my long-felt
OL,9,Fand profound sense of shame".
OL,11,FBishop Conway has now come under
OL,12,Fpressure over what he did after he
OL,13,Fbecame aware of allegations against
OL,14,FSmyth.
