OL,3,CBishop 'sorry' for failing to
OL,4,C'rigorously' pursue abuse claims
OL,6,FIn a statement he said he "made a
OL,7,Fdetailed disclosure to (the
OL,8,FArchbishop's office) Lambeth Palace
OL,9,Fand contacted the relevant diocese in
OL,10,FSouth Africa to alert them to the
OL,11,Fissue" when the claims were raised
OL,12,Fwith him.
OL,14,FHe said he understood the matter had
OL,15,Fbeen reported to police in the UK.
