OL,3,CBishop 'sorry' for failing to
OL,4,C'rigorously' pursue abuse claims
OL,6,FThe Bishop said: "I am clear that I
OL,7,Fdid all within my authority as a
OL,8,FBishop of the Church of England,
OL,9,Fbearing in mind that I had no
OL,10,Fauthority over an entirely independent
OL,11,Fprovince on another continent."
OL,13,FHowever, he added: "I acknowledge
OL,14,Ffully that my fault was in not
OL,15,Frigorously pursuing Lambeth about that
OL,16,Fprovince-to-province communication,
OL,17,Fand for this I am deeply sorry."
